desc: My name is Rasheen Rodgers but everyone just calls me Sheenie. I am the owner of Rodgers Events and Decor. Rodgers Events and Decor is a reputable party rental business that specializes in birthday parties and baby showers. The family owned business is dedicated to providing a unique experience for our clients.

layout.text:
From wedding functions to birthday parties or baby showers,
we offer full range of party rental services that scale to your needs & budget.
